      "text": "AIT-AX210 supports the latest WiFi 6E (IEEE 802.11ax) with special features like OFDMA, 1024QAM and MU-MIMO. Module includes also Bluetooth 5.2, and is backward compatible and operates in 2.4, 5 and 6 GHz bands."
